pe":"Mono","hullConstruction":"GRP","amenities":[{"label":"Washer ","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Dryer","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Generator","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Dishwasher","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Ice maker,","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Condaria Air Conditioning","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Eberspacher heating in all cabins","quantity":"1"}],"toys":[{"label":"Stand up paddle board","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Seabob","quantity":"1"},{"label":"E-foiler","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Snorkelling equipment","quantity":"4"}],"entertainment":["B&G H5000 Instruments","5g wifi mesh network","Widescreen smart TV","Bose Sound system","Playstation"],"tenders":["4m tender with a 30hp engine"]},"crew":[{"name":"Richard Robinson","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::e9a38e30-5265-11f0-8619-c951789ae5cc::assets::1e933420-526a-11f0-bf4d-6dd24b600780/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Richard grew up sailing with his family on the West Coast of Scotland. As a holder of a Commercially Endorsed Yacht Master Ocean license, Richard and been captain on various Maxi Yachts over the past 10 years and can be described as an outgoing, but steady handed and resourceful seaman with a strong technical- and mechanical skillset. Apart from being a professional Yachtsman, Richard loves to surf in his spare time. \n\nAdditional Info inc Certificates:\n• Languages: French (conversational)\n• RYA Yachtmaster Ocean (Commercially\nendorsed)\n• ENG 1 Medical\n• GMDSS (GOC)\n• PADI Open Water Diver"},{"name":"Zuzana Zigmundova","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::e9a38e30-5265-11f0-8619-c951789ae5cc::assets::5b674170-526a-11f0-bf4d-6dd24b600780/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Zuzana has been a private chef onboard yachts for over 13 years and has sailed in the Caribbean, Pacific, Mediterranean, US East coast and South America. Her style of cooking has been inspired from all the various destinations she has sailed. Whilst being adaptive and accommodating to any dietary needs guests might have, Zuzana loves to use healthy sustainable local produce whenever this is possible. Zuzana is passionate about photography and publishes her own food blog.\n\nAdditional Info inc Certificates:\n• Languages: English, Slovak and Czech (fluent)\nGreek, French, Spanish (conversational)\n• Ayurveda Nutrition Certification\n• Food Safety Hygiene Certification\n• Registered Yoga Teacher (200 & 300)\n• Seafarer Medical Certification , STCW"},{"name":"Beatrice Williams","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::e9a38e30-5265-11f0-8619-c951789ae5cc::assets::006e6ae0-526b-11f0-aa18-11dbce2b1e81/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Beatrice’s sailing career started in dinghies and progressed to sail training ships and luxury yachts. A true sailor at heart, she taught crew, young and old to sail and compete in multiple Tall Ships races, latterly as the First Mate of an 111 year old pilot cutter.\n\nGaining her Yachtmaster at the age of 19, and with an Atlantic and multiple North Sea crossings under her belt Beatrice is a confident sailor in all types of weather. She brings a sense of fun, adventure and a cheery smile to everything she does on board. When she’s not on the water Beatrice is a keen field hockey player, fitness enthusiast and traveller.\n\nAdditional Info inc Certificates:\n• RYA Yachtmaster Offshore (Commercially\nendorsed)\n• ENG 1 Medical\n• PB L2\n• STCW Basic Safety Training"}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"EUR","price":4000000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":4000000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"EUR","price":4200000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":4200000,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"High Season","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2026-07-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-08-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2027-07-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2027-08-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2028-07-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2028-08-31T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"currency":"EUR","charterFee":4200000,"inputAmountTaxed":"EXCLUSIVE","note":"